&lt;li&gt;Utilize judgement and best practices to complete research, writing, and editing of cases of different products, scopes, jurisdictions, and complexity.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Determine and escalate identified risk factors to case manager.&lt;/li&gt;
