&lt;div class=&quot;content-intro&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Who We Are:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Exiger transforms supply chains into a strategic advantage, advancing our mission to make the world a safer and more transparent place to succeed. Our&lt;span data-ogsb=&quot;rgb(255, 255, 255)&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;AI platform, 1Exiger&lt;/span&gt;, delivers instant visibility into complex supplier ecosystems, leveraging proprietary data and advanced AI to surface risk, automate compliance, and unlock&lt;span class=&quot;Apple-converted-space&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ogsb=&quot;rgb(255, 255, 255)&quot;&gt;efficiencies and cost savings to strengthen long-term resilience&lt;/span&gt;. Trusted by 550+ global customers, including Fortune 500 companies and U.S. government agencies, Exiger is a recognized, award-winning leader in supply chain AI and a FedRAMP® authorized provider to the federal government.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;Data Services team members deliver on and embody Exiger’s purpose daily – making the world a safer place to do business – through researching, writing, reviewing, editing and developing reputational due diligence that inform business decisions for many of the world’s largest and most influential organizations and institutions globally. Data Services team members are on the front lines helping our clients understand with whom they are doing business and identify potential risks associated with such business relationships.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Key Responsibilities&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Work to successfully resolve issues at the Conference and Team levels.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;s&gt; &lt;/s&gt;Drive Conference growth based on a range of defined metrics and qualifications.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Foster team environment and drive Conference success through setting clear accountabilities and continuous mentor ship and coaching teammates to advance their growth, development and research expertise.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Coach others to problem solve and manage others.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Facilitate trainings to advance teammates’ technical and professional growth and development, in coordination with the training team.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Propose and implement solutions to improve existing policies, procedures, processes and standards that provide tangible value to clients, Diligence and/or Exiger.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Prepared to present findings to clients and answer their questions.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;All other business activities including but not limited to in the research and delivery and tech of our products and services.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Conducts weekly or based on needs meetings with their direct reports, in order to provide updates and gathering feedback.&lt;/li&gt;
